              <Comments>In a number of languages there is no way of speaking of ‘supernatural powers’ or ‘supernatural forces.’ Reference can only be made to such powers in terms of kinds of spirit beings; therefore, one may render στοιχεῖα[b] in {S:05100202000014} as ‘those spirits that have power’ or ‘those spirits which control.’</Comments>
